{"id":232920056,"title":"請大家飼養毛孩，特別是貓咪務必要預防心絲蟲","content":"我發現，有些養貓咪的飼主，似乎沒有固定讓貓咪點滴劑的習慣。\n\n所以，想跟大家分享一下，貓咪要記得點滴劑，特別是夏天，最主要是預防蚊子叮咬傳染的心絲蟲。\n\n貓咪，目前得到心絲蟲，基本上不太能治癒，而且，飼主要發現，通常都是貓咪有異常，或是蟲體夠大，已經寄生到心臟，才會發現。此時已經來不及了。\n\n夏天是蚊蟲較多的時節，家裡很難100%避免蚊子入侵，叮咬毛孩。\n\n假設想瞭解心絲蟲對貓咪的影響，可以搜尋  貓 心絲蟲  爬文。\n\n我家貓目前點的是寵愛滴劑，還有其他廠牌可以選擇，請大家洽詢獸醫。\n\n附上我家的美女，希望大家的毛孩，都能健康過好年。\n\nhttps://i.imgur.com/x0rN6fD.jpg\n\nhttps://i.imgur.com/TESYg84.jpg","excerpt":"我發現，有些養貓咪的飼主，似乎沒有固定讓貓咪點滴劑的習慣。所以，想跟大家分享一下，貓咪要記得點滴劑，特別是夏天，最主要是預防蚊子叮咬傳染的心絲蟲。貓咪，目前得到心絲蟲，基本上不太能治癒，而且，飼主要發","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"7ee21581-1307-4ba9-b9dc-82028bdcca49","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-19T12:40:46.037Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-19T12:40:46.037Z","commentCount":16,"likeCount":16,"tags":[],"topics":["貓","心絲蟲","預防","飼養"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"寵物","forumAlias":"pet","school":"女王大大","department":"f224766","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":16}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/x0rN6fD.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/TESYg84.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"c9aea88e-988a-4663-b77d-800d49113b3c","url":"https://i.imgur.com/x0rN6fDl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/x0rN6fDl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/x0rN6fDl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-19T12:40:46.037Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-19T12:40:46.037Z"},{"id":"c9aea88e-988a-4663-b77d-800d49113b3c","url":"https://i.imgur.com/x0rN6fD.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/x0rN6fD","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/x0rN6fDl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-19T12:40:46.037Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-19T12:40:46.037Z"},{"id":"0266aa1f-